{"title":"Vitus E-Mythique LT is a Long Travel eMTB Priced Below $4k","link":"https://bikerumor.com/vitus-e-mythique-long-travel-emtb-affordable/","date":1691526094000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-hero-feathure.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT hero feature\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-hero-feathure.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-hero-feathure-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-hero-feathure-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-hero-feathure-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-hero-feathure-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-hero-feathure-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>Adding to its extensive line of performance eMTB, Vitus Bikes introduced the new E-Mythique LT. There have been a lot of new electric mountain bikes introduced lately, but the E-Mythique looks to bring the barrier to entry even lower for the long-travel crowd. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-standing.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-standing-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT standing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-standing-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-standing-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-standing-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-standing-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-standing-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-standing.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Vitus Bikes</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The E-Mythique LT will be available in three different spec options, VR, VRS, and VRX. All will be powered by a Bafang M510 drive unit custom-tuned for this bicycle.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-climbing.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-climbing-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT climbing\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-climbing-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-climbing-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-climbing-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-climbing-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-climbing-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-climbing.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Owing to the LT name, the new bike is long-travel (170mm/160mm) and a mixed-wheel variation of the analog Mythique. The E-Mythique LT incorporates learnings from the current E-Sommet range and creates a bicycle that is ready to ride everything a modern enduro bike can handle. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Vitus partnered with Befang and chose to use their M510 drive unit which has a maximum torque of 95Nm and a competitive unit weight. Vitus also worked with Bafang to custom-tune the M510, effectively “cherry-picking the best features” for the E-Mythique LT.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-icy.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-icy-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT icy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-icy-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-icy-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-icy-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-icy-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-icy-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-icy.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The M510 is powered by an integrated 630Wh battery and display unit with 5 power modes – Eco, Eco Plus, Trail, Boost, and Race. These modes give the rider options for adjusting range and on-trail performance. These days you can find bigger batteries than 630Wh, but rarely at this price. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-gettin-shreddy.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-gettin-shreddy-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT gettin' shreddy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-gettin-shreddy-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-gettin-shreddy-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-gettin-shreddy-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-gettin-shreddy-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-gettin-shreddy-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-gettin-shreddy.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-rocky.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-rocky-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT rocky\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-rocky-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-rocky-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-rocky-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-rocky-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-rocky-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-rocky.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The E-Mythique LT Geometry</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-GEO.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"417\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-GEO-800x417.jpg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT GEO\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-GEO-800x417.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-GEO-297x155.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-GEO-120x63.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-GEO-768x400.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-GEO.jpg 1200w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>The E-Mythique LT Line Up</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>For the base model LT VR, you can pick up an E-Mythique for under $4k. Even at the top end, you’re still looking at a bike below $5k, which is highly competitive for the category. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-hero.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-hero-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT VR hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-hero-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-hero-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-hero-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-hero-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-hero-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-hero.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Vitus E-Mystique LT VR </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3><strong>E-Mythique LT VR</strong> – Retail, Highlights, Features, and Specs</h3>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Retail: </strong>$3,699</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Highlights:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>SR Suntour Zeron36 &amp; Deluxe Select R suspension</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Smooth Bafang M510 motor produces 250W max power and 95Nm torque</li>\n\n\n\n<li>630Wh internal battery</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Wide range Microshift Advent X 1×10 speed drivetrain Powerful Tektro 4 piston hydraulic disc brakes Tubeless-ready WTB rims with grippy Vee Tires</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-fork.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"1200\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-fork-800x1200.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT VR fork\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-fork-800x1200.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-fork-200x300.jpeg 200w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-fork-80x120.jpeg 80w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-fork-768x1152.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-fork.jpeg 853w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-cockpit.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-cockpit-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT VR cockpit\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-cockpit-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-cockpit-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-cockpit-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-cockpit-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-cockpit-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-cockpit.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-der.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-der-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT VR rear der\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-der-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-der-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-der-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-der-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-der-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-der.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-sus.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-sus-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT VR rear sus\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-sus-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-sus-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-sus-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-sus-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-sus-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-rear-sus.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>E-Mythique electric enduro platform – </strong>Internal battery frame design with new Bafang M510 drive unit, Vitus optimized suspension kinematics, and geometry.</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Frame material – </strong>6061-T6 aluminum</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Color – </strong>Black Quartz</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Available size – </strong>S, M, L, XL</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Wheel size – </strong>Mullet – 29” front / 27.5” rear</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Suspension travel (MTB) – </strong>160mm front, 160mm rear</li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Intended use – </strong>Enduro</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Specs: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-Spec-sheet.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"441\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-Mystique-LT-VR-Spec-sheet-800x441.jpg\" alt=\"Vitus E-Mystique LT VR Spec sheet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Vitus-E-My